                <div class="w-full h-max rounded p-6 relative flex flex-col justify-end">
                    <h5 class="font-sans antialiased font-bold text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white mb-2">Search and Discovery</h5>
                    <p class="font-sans antialiased text-base text-white/80">Website visitors today demand a frictionless user expericence â€” especially when using search. Because of the hight standards we tend to offer.</p>
